Class FrequencyAnalyzer.ColumnDataFileProcessor

    public static class FrequencyAnalyzer.ColumnDataFileProcessor
extends FrequencyAnalyzer.AbstractCorpusProcessor
    A corpus processor that counts preprocessed data. The lines of the file must consist of columns separated by whitespace. One column in each line represents a word, and another column represents a count of the occurrences of that word. The column used for each is configurable, and all other columns are ignored. Any line that does not contain one of the specified columns is ignored.
